OL,6,FAcross Northern Ireland classrooms,
OL,7,Fschool halls and canteens are in
OL,8,Fdesperate need of replacement.
OL,10,FUTV has been seen figures which show
OL,11,Fnearly 70 schools are awaiting new
OL,12,FbuildingsJSome schools are set to wait
OL,13,Fup to 15 years for new buildings to
OL,14,Fopen since their projects were first
OL,15,Fannounced.
OL,17,FEducation Minister Paul Givan has said
OL,18,Fhe is frustrated at the situation and
OL,19,Fneeds more funding.
