OL,3,CAlmost 70 schools in NI awaiting
OL,4,Credevelopment for up to 15 years
OL,6,F68 schools in Northern Ireland are
OL,7,Fawaiting new buildings or campus
OL,8,Fredevelopments.
OL,10,FFigures seen by UTV show that almost a
OL,11,Fthird (21) of those plans are on hold.
OL,13,FAll of the schools are at different
OL,14,Fstages between design and construction
OL,15,Fand many are frustrated at the pace of
OL,16,Fchange.
OL,18,F3 other schools are in development
OL,19,Fstage.
