OL,6,FOne high school in Co Armagh and one
OL,7,Fprimary school in Co Down are
OL,8,Fearmarked to be completed by 2032 -
OL,9,Fthe longest wait of all.
OL,11,FJustin McCamphill from teaching union
OL,12,FNASWUT told UTV: "We know education in
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland has been a dire in a
OL,14,Fdire state for quite some time.
OL,16,F"As well as the pressures around
OL,17,Fcapital funding for new schools, we
OL,18,Falso have a massive backlog in
OL,19,Fmaintenance.
